                <p>Hypertech Power Chips are direct replacements for the stock chips in 1981-1995 GM vehicles. The Power Chip contains the Hypertech Power Tuning data that controls the engine’s air/fuel ratio and spark advance for maximum power and performance plus, potential gas mileage improvements. Power Chips can be installed easily, using only hand tools. Call for more information or specific applications.</p>

                <p>The Street Runner™ Power Chip is designed for daily street driving or competition in unmodified vehicles using a stock thermostat.</p>

                <p>The ThermoMaster™ Power Chip is designed to be used with a 160° or 180° PowerStat thermostat.</p>

